50
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:24,400
事实是  你的好感度是我的二倍
Well, the truth is, your favorables are double what mine are,

51
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,180
那我们就给人们他们想要的吧
so let's give the people what they want.

52
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:28,880
好吧  如果你觉得这样有帮助的话
Well, if you think it will help.

53
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,830
肯定会的
I know it will.

54
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,370
你们准备演讲稿了吗  有没有问题清单
Do you have a speech prepared? Do you have issue papers?

55
00:02:32,370 --> 00:02:33,630
一切都在会议室里
Everything is in the conference room.

56
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:34,840
那我们就开始吧
Let's get started, then.

57
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:42,380
您有没有看过那个清单
Have you had a chance to go over the list...

58
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:43,490
雷米的接替者的名单
of replacements for Remy?

59
